# env files — real values stay local (.env, .env.local). The placeholder
# template at the repo root (.env.example) IS committed so a fresh clone
# has the canonical list. The leading slash on the exception keeps it
# root-only so stray .env.example copies elsewhere stay ignored.
.env*
!/.env.example

